===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|Burgh (Masters)}}
Burgh forms a [[sync pair]] with {{p|Leavanny}} and {{p|Togepi}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. Burgh became a playable sync pair on June 18, 2020.

Burgh has also made notable appearances in one of the game's main stories, the [[villain arc]]. 

